| Pest Species                   | Common name                      | Host Crop and Distribution                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|--------------------------------|----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Microcephalothrips abdominalis | Sunflower thrips                 | Various species from Asteraceae, notably sunflowers. Breeds in flowers, sometimes causing flower distortion.